PrecisEnactment of an ORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (2002, No. 01, LIARD FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which (a) prohibits the staking of mineral claims or prospecting in specific areas in the Yukon until March 31, 2004, and (b) repeals the Prohibition of Entry on Certain Lands Order, No. 4 of 2000.

precis:
Enactment of an ORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON
TERRITORY (2002, No. 01, LIARD FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which (a) prohibits
the staking of mineral claims or prospecting in specific areas in the Yukon
until March 31, 2004, and (b) repeals the Prohibition of Entry on Certain
Lands Order, No. 4 of 2000.
